timeline.bodyText:
Unfortunately, I don't think this will work for nested fields, for example the following fails on this PR:
PUT /_index_template/generic
{
  "index_patterns": ["logs-*"],
  "data_stream": {
    "timestamp_field": "foo.timestamp"
  },
  "template": {
    "mappings": {
      "properties": {
        "foo": {
          "properties": {
            "timestamp": {
              "type": "date"
            }
          }
        }
      }
    }
  }
}

